docs: atomic primitives plan refinements, ADR-010 offline strategy, supporting plans

Atomic Primitives Plan (atomic-primitives-analysis.md):
- Rename DataTable to DisplayGrid (disambiguate from rejected section-level pattern)
- Tighten Grid vs. Section Decision Tree with hard contract boundary
- Add 3.6 AtomicComposite Performance Contract (depth 6, children 20, nodes 50)
- Add Phase 4b: Tier 2 Evaluation Gate with entry criteria and checklist
- Add Phase 6: Governance Document Updates with per-doc checklists

ADR-010: Offline and Degraded Connectivity
- Option B (stale-while-offline) recommended
- Leverages ADR-004 cacheability classes and platform HTTP cache
- Live sections show placeholder; others show stale with timestamp

Technical Proposal updates:
- Add 9r offline/degraded connectivity requirement
- Update revision history, requirement status table, next steps

New supporting plans:
- Accessibility plan (6 phases, cross-cutting atomic + semantic layers)
- Action failure semantics plan (4 phases, behavior contract)

Phase 1 implementation (atomic renderers):
- Android: AtomicRouter + 9 primitive renderers, AtomicElement model/parser
- Web: AtomicRouter + 9 primitive components, types, index
- Both platforms: SectionRouter updated to delegate AtomicComposite sections
